name: IZ*ONE_Yabuki Nako
description:
Introduction: Yabuki Nako is an active member of the Japanese girl group HKT48 Team H under EMI Records and a former member of the South Korean-Japanese girl group IZ*ONE under Off The Record Entertainment. source

Fourth LoRA with controlled amount of datasets, probably my best work so far, at the moment, this is what I used:

Model: ChilloutMix_NiPrunedFp32Fix (works best to handle the hairs)/ Basil_mix_fixed (works pretty good as well)
Sampling: DPM++ SDE Karras
Sampling: 20 to 30
Hires steps: 20
Size: 512x768
CFG Scale: 4 (recommended), but still getting good result with 7
LoRA strength: 0.8(best result), 0.9-1 (good result, but will have some noise with the hairs)
Face restoration: GFPGAN 0.5

CLIP skip: 2
Use the usual VAE

Upscaler: Nearest , upscale by x2
Denoising: 0.49

Hires fix is optional

Highly encouraged to use CLIP skip 2

It's not perfect, but I hope this LoRA is worth your time and the time I spent making this.

If you feel like supporting, do leave a tip at my kofi page


It took a lot of hours of hard work and dedication, so any kinds of support is very much appreciated :) :)

Thank you so much!!

Legal & Risk

Please do not post any NSFW images in the review.

It is prohibited to use this model for commercial purposes and any scenarios of illegal acts and purposes.

本人原则上不支持使用此模型生成任何成人内容。用户在使用本模型时，请务必遵守当地法律法规，勿侵犯他人的名誉权、隐私权或肖像权。

I generally do not support the use of this model to generate any adult content. When using this model, users should abide by local laws and regulations and shall not violate any other's right to reputation, privacy or portrait.

私は一般的に、このモデルを使用して成人コンテンツを生成することをサポートしません。 このモデルを使用する場合は、ユーザーは当地の法律や規制を守り、他人の名誉権、プライバシー権または肖像権を侵害しないようにしなければなりません。
